        public SpinOption(String name,
                  Integer defaultValue,
                  Integer min,
                  Integer max)
           throws NullPointerException
        Constructs a spin option instance. None of the parameters can be null.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the option. Cannot be null.
        defaultValue - The value of the spin option by default. Cannot be null.
        min - The minimum accepted value for the option (inclusive). Cannot be null.
        max - The maximum accepted value for the option (inclusive). Cannot be null.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If any of the parameters are null.
